dct_title_s: Dominia Anglorum in America Septentrionali. Specialibus mappis Londini primum a Mollio edita, nunc recusa ab Homannianis Hered = Die Gros-Britannische Colonie-Lænder in Nord-America...
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Sheet title in Latin and German. Individual map titles and text in German. Maps in English and German. From the authors' Atlas geographicus maior. 1753-59 [i.e. 1781, v. 1, 1759] v. 1, no. 141. Includes text and glossary.
